text: Woody Town Chūō Station (ウッディタウン中央駅, ウッディタウンちゅうおうえき) is a railway station of Kobe Electric Railway in Sanda, Hyōgo, Japan. Chūō means Central in Japanese. == Adjacent stations == ; Kobe Electric Railway : Kōen-Toshi Line :: Minami Woody Town - Woody Town Chūō Station ==Other websites== Category:Railway stations in Japan Category:Hyōgo Prefecture
